<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205823>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 – 31. S. (M.) schizostylum Chen and Zhang, sp. nov. 20. Female genitalia; 21. Female cibarium; 22. Female sensory vesicle; 23. Gonocoxite and gonostylus of male; 24. Ventral plate; 25. Median sclerite; 26. Paramere; 27. Cocoon in dorsal view; 28. Filaments; 29. Larval head capsule in ventral view; 30. Larval mandible; 31. Larval anal sclerite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

